<h2 style="text-align:center;color: blue;font-size:30px;margin-bottom: 30px;">The Virtual Zoo</h2>
<p style="font-size:20px;margin-bottom: 30px;text-align:center;color: rgb(214, 122, 127);">The VIZ project is a virtual zoo that came to you.It is a fun way of learning and understading different things.<br>
As you can't visit various places and see the variety of animals, we made them come to you.</p>
